msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Descriptives"
msgstr "Deskriptif"

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Descriptive Statistics"
msgstr "Statistik Deskriptif"

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Explore the data with tables and plots"
msgstr "Eksplorasi data dengan tabel dan plot"

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Time Series Descriptives"
msgstr "Deskriptif Seri Waktu"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Time Series Descriptives allows the user to obtain descriptive statistics "
"and descriptive plots for univariate time-series."
msgstr ""
"Deskriptif Seri Waktu mengizinkan pengguna untuk memperoleh statistik "
"deskriptif dan diagram deskriptif untuk seri waktu univariat."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Variable"
msgstr "Variabel"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "A variable that is measured repeatedly over time."
msgstr "Variabel yang diukur secara berulang dari waktu."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Waktu"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Optional. Can either be an ordinal variable indicating the order of the "
"observations, or a text variable indicating the date/time stamp of the "
"observations. Combined date and time values should be in the standard format "
"'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS', where seconds (':SS') can also be omitted. Date-only "
"values should be in the format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. If a time variable is not "
"supplied, the row order of the data is used."
msgstr ""
"Opsional. Dapat baik variabel ordinal mengindikasikan urutan observasi, atau "
"variabel teks mengindikasikan tanggal/stempel waktu observasi. Nilai tanggal "
"dan waktu terkombinasi seharusnya dalam format standar 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:"
"SS', di mana detik (':SS') juga dapat dihilangkan. Nilai hanya tanggal "
"seharusnya dalam format 'YYYY-MM-DD'. Jika variabel waktu tidak disertakan, "
"urutan baris data digunakan."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Transpose descriptives table"
msgstr "Transposkan tabel deskriptif"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Filter by"
msgstr "Filter berdasarkan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Filters the time series so only a specific range will be used for further "
"analyses. Row number refers to the row number in the spreadsheet. If a "
"'Time' variable is supplied it is also possible to filter by time index or "
"date, depending on the format of the 'Time' variable."
msgstr ""
"Menyaring seri waktu sehingga hanya rentang tertentu akan digunakan untuk "
"analisis lebih lanjut. Nomor baris mengacu nomor baris di lembar kerja. Jika "
"variabel 'Waktu' disertakan itu juga dapat menyaring berdasarkan indeks "
"waktu atau tanggal, tergantung pada format variabel 'Waktu'."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Row number"
msgstr "Angka baris"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Mulai"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "End"
msgstr "Selesai"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Time index"
msgstr "Indeks waktu"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Tanggal"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Plots"
msgstr "Diagram"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Time series plot"
msgstr "Diagram seri waktu"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Plots the dependent variable (y-axis) over time (x-axis)."
msgstr "Mendiagram variabel dependen (sumbu-y) terhadap waktu (sumbu-x)."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Points"
msgstr "Titik"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Line"
msgstr "Garis"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Both"
msgstr "Keduanya"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "Distribusi"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Density"
msgstr "Kepadatan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Histogram"
msgstr "Histogram"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Tidak Ada"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Lag plot"
msgstr "Diagram penundaan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Plots the dependent variable (y-axis) against a lagged version of itself (x-"
"axis). The lag stands for the amount of observations in between the "
"dependent variable and the lagged version of itself. The regression line is "
"the autoregression at the specified lag."
msgstr ""
"Mendiagram variabel dependen (sumbu-y) terhadap versi tertundanya (sumbu-x). "
"Penundaan menunjukkan jumlah observasi antara variabel dependen dan versi "
"tertundanya. Garis regresi adalah regresi otomatis pada penundaan yang "
"ditentukan."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Lag"
msgstr "Penundaan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Add regression line"
msgstr "Tambahkan garis regresi"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Smooth"
msgstr "Halus"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "Linear"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Confidence interval"
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Autocorrelation function"
msgstr "Fungsi korelasi otomatis"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Maximum lag"
msgstr "Penundaan maksimum"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Zero lag"
msgstr "Nol penundaan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid ""
"Plots the autocorrelation for a specified number of lags. The confidence "
"interval may be given assuming either a white noise process, or assuming for "
"a lag q a moving average process of order q - 1."
msgstr ""
"Mendiagram korelasi otomatis untuk jumlah penundaan tertentu. Interval "
"kepercayaan mungkin diberikan mengasumsikan baik proses noise putih, atau "
"mengasumsikan untuk penundaan q proses rata-rata perpindahan urutan q - 1."

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Based on white noise"
msgstr "Berdasarkan noise putih"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Based on moving average"
msgstr "Berdasarkan rata-rata perpindahan"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Partial autocorrelation function"
msgstr "Fungsi korelasi otomatis parsial"

msgctxt "DescriptivesTimeSeriesForm|"
msgid "Plots the partial autocorrelation for a specified number of lags."
msgstr "Mendiagram korelasi otomatis parsial untuk jumlah penundaan tertentu."

