"RM<br>reference_lines: Garis referensi<br>identity_line: Garis "
"identitas<br>point_labels: Label titik"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"You can set the order of the added geometric/data layers here, similar to "
"the example shown in the text field.\n"
"The order of the layers is defined from left to right—meaning the rightmost "
"layer will be drawn on top."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengatur urutan lapisan geometris/data yang ditambahkan di sini, "
"mirip dengan contoh yang ditunjukkan di kolom teks.\n"
"Urutan lapisan ditentukan dari kiri ke kanan—berarti lapisan paling kanan "
"akan digambar di atas."

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Layer order"
msgstr "Urutan lapisan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "point, boxplot"
msgstr "titik, diagram kotak"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Adjust how faceted panels share scales, axes and space. <b>Scale and axis "
"settings</b> decide whether panels use the same range, which axis lines are "
"drawn and where labels appear. <b>Layout settings</b> control panel sizes, "
"the position of the highest-value table, optional marginal plots and custom "
"axis titles"
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan bagaimana panel berfaset membagikan skala, sumbu dan spasi. "
"<b>Pengaturan skala dan sumbu</b> memutuskan apakah panel menggunakan "
"rentang sama, yang mana garis sumbu digambar dan di mana label muncul. "
"<b>Pengaturan tata letak</b> mengontrol ukuran panel, posisi tabel nilai-"
"tertinggi, diagram margin opsional dan judul sumbu kustom"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Choose whether facet panels share a common scale (<i>fixed</i>) or get "
"individual ranges"
msgstr ""
"Pilih apakah panel faset membagikan skala umum (<i>tetap</i>) atau "
"mendapatkan rentang individu"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Decide which facet panels display axis lines"
msgstr "Putuskan yang mana panel faset menampilkan garis sumbu"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Control which tick-label texts are shown"
msgstr "Kontrol yang mana teks tabel-centang ditampilkan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Controls where the summary table of highest values is placed inside each "
"facet"
msgstr ""
"Mengontrol di mana tabel ringkasan nilai tertinggi ditempatkan di dalam "
"setiap faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Allow facet panels to stretch freely along X, Y or both axes"
msgstr ""
"Izinkan panel faset untuk meregang secara bebas dengan sumbu X, Y atau kedua"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Adds aggregated rows/columns at the edges of the facet grid"
msgstr "Menambahkan baris/kolom teragregasi di tepi kisi faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Arrange panels when a grid variable is mapped. <b>Layout settings</b> set "
"the facet grid’s rows, columns and where the highest-values table appears, "
"<b>Scales and strip settings</b> decide whether panels share axes and where "
"the facet label strip is placed"
msgstr ""
"Susun panel ketika variabel kisi dipetakan. <b>Pengaturan tata telak</b> "
"mengatur baris, kolom kisi faset, dan di mana tabel nilai-tertinggi muncul, "
"<b>Pengaturan skala dan strip</b> memutuskan apakah panel membagikan sumbu "
"dan di mana strip label faset ditempatkan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed number of facet columns; 0 lets the layout pick automatically"
msgstr ""
"Jumlah tetap kolom faset; 0 membiarkan tata letak memilih secara otomatis"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed number of facet rows; 0 lets the layout pick automatically"
msgstr ""
"Jumlah tetap baris faset; 0 membiarkan tata letak memilih secara otomatis"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Choose the corner where the summary table of highest values is drawn"
msgstr "Pilih sudut di mana tabel ringkasan nilai tertinggi digambargan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed panels share axes; free panels get independent X and/or Y scales"
msgstr ""
"Panel tetap membagikan sumbu; panel bebas mendapatkan skala X dan/atau Y "
"independen"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Location of the facet label strip"
msgstr "Lokasi strip label faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Add brackets with P values to show pairwise significance.\n"
"Set colour, text size and vertical spacing, then list each comparison in the "
"table below"
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan kurung dengan nilai P untuk menampilkan signifikan berpasangan.\n"
"Atur warna, ukuran teks dan penspasian vertikal, kemudian cantumkan setiap "
"perbandingan dalam tabel di bawah"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Colour and font size of the P-value text"
msgstr "Warna dan ukuran huruf teks nilai-P"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Named or hex colour for the P value text"
msgstr "Warna bernama atau heks untuk teks nilai P"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Font size of the P value text"
msgstr "Ukuran huruf teks nilai P"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Starting height and step between stacked brackets (data units)"
msgstr "Tinggi dan langkah awal antara kurung tertumpuk (unit data)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Initial vertical position for the first bracket"
msgstr "Posisi vertikal inisial untuk kurung pertama"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Vertical gap between successive brackets"
msgstr "Jarak vertikal antara kurung berturut-turut"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Labels of the two groups being compared"
msgstr "Label dari dua grup sedang dibandingkan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Enter the P value (e.g. 0.03) or a significance symbol (*, **, ***). <b>Tip "
"length</b> is the size of the bracket tips; <b>Bracket size</b> is the "
"horizontal width"
msgstr ""
"Masukkan nilai P (mis., 0.03) atau simbol signifikan (*, **, ***). "
"<b>Panjang tip</b> adalah ukuran tip kurung; <b>Ukuran kurung</b> adalah "
"lebar horizontal"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "P value"
msgstr "Nilai P"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Select the facet (group/column/row/grid) where the bracket should appear"
msgstr "Pilih faset (grup/kolom/baris/kisi) di mana kurung harus muncul"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Draw manual comparison lines (e.g., <b>min–max bars</b> or custom contrasts) "
"with optional text labels"
msgstr ""
"Gambar garis perbandingan manual (mis., <b>batang min-maks</b> atau kontras "
"kustom) dengan label teks opsional"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Note: If custom Y-Axis limits are set, the starting\n"
"position for the Y-Axis start and end values must fall within the defined "
"interval"
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Jika batas Sumbu-Y kustom diatur, posisi\n"
"awal untuk nilai awal dan akhir Sumbu-Y harus mencakup dalam interval "
"tertentu"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Define one comparison line with optional label, coordinates and appearance"
msgstr ""
"Definisikan satu garis perbandingan dengan label opsional, koordinat dan "
"penampilan"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Text shown near the line (leave empty for no label)"
msgstr ""
"Teks ditampilkan mendekati garis (biarkan kosong untuk tidak ada label)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Start/end coordinates and facet location"
msgstr "Koordinat awal/akhir dan lokasi faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line start on X axis"
msgstr "Awal garis pada sumbu X"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line end on X axis"
msgstr "Akhir garis pada sumbu X"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line start on Y axis"
msgstr "Awal garis pada sumbu Y"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line end on Y axis"
msgstr "Akhir garis pada sumbu Y"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet column (for split layouts)"
msgstr "Kolom faset (untuk tata letak terpisah)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet row (for split layouts)"
msgstr "Baris faset (untuk tata letak terpisah)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet grid cell"
msgstr "Sel kisi faset"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet column (RM)"
msgstr "Kolom faset (RM)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet row (RM)"
msgstr "Baris faset (RM)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet grid cell (RM)"
msgstr "Sel kisi faset (RM)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line colour and label styling"
msgstr "Warna garis dan gaya label"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Named or hex colour for the line"
msgstr "Warna bernama atau heks untuk garis"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Font size of the label text"
msgstr "Ukuran huruf teks label"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Vertical offset between the line and its label (data units)"
msgstr "Pergeseran vertikal antara garis dan labelnya (unit data)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Combine multiple plots in custom grids. <b>Arrange plots by column</b> "
"builds the top part of the layout, <b>Arrange plots by row</b> builds the "
"bottom. Specify plot IDs, relative sizes and optional common legends"
msgstr ""
"Kombinasikan beberapa diagram di kisi kustom. <b>Susun diagram berdasarkan "
"kolom</b> membangun bagian atas tata letak, <b>Susun diagram berdasarkan "
"baris</b> membangun bawah. Tentukan ID diagram, ukuran relatif dan legenda "
"umum opsional"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Comma-separated numbers that set the width of each column"
msgstr "Angka yang dipisahkan koma yang mengatur tinggi setiap kolom"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Comma-separated IDs referencing earlier plots"
msgstr "ID yang dipisahkan koma mereferensikan diagram sebelumnya"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Relative heights of plots within this column"
msgstr "Tinggi relatif diagram dalam baris ini"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Optional plot labels (A, B, …)"
msgstr "Label diagram opsional (A, B, …)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Merge legends of all plots in this column"
msgstr "Gabungkan legenda semua diagram di kolom ini"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Comma-separated numbers that set the height of each row"
msgstr "Angka yang dipisahkan koma yang mengatur tinggi setiap baris"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Relative widths of plots within this row"
msgstr "Lebar relatif diagram dalam baris ini"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Merge legends of all plots in this row"
msgstr "Gabungkan legenda semua diagram di baris ini"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Font size of subplot labels"
msgstr "Ukuran huruf label subdiagram"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Horizontal offset of labels (0–1, relative to plot width)"
msgstr "Pergeseran horizontal label (0–1, relatif ke lebar diagram)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Vertical offset of labels (0–1, relative to plot height)"
msgstr "Pergeseran vertikal label (0–1, relatif ke tinggi diagram)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Relative heights of columns or widths of rows when combining column and row "
"layouts"
msgstr ""
"Tinggi relatif kolom atau lebar baris ketika menggabungkan tata letak kolom "
"dan baris"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Overall width of the assembled layout (pixels)"
msgstr "Lebar keseluruhan tata letak terakit (piksel)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Overall height of the assembled layout (pixels)"
msgstr "Tinggi keseluruhan dari tata letak terakit (piksel)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Gap between plots inside the layout (pixels)"
msgstr "Jarak antara diagram dalam tata letak (piksel)"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Place a single shared legend for all plots in the layout"
msgstr ""
"Tempatkan legenda yang dibagikan tunggal untuk semua diagram dalam tata letak"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Box statistics"
msgstr "Statistik kotak"

msgctxt "Description|"
msgid "Plot Builder"
msgstr "Pembangun Diagram"
